/***** Global Balloon Design -- START *****/
/* Title text */
.walkme-custom-balloon-title{
	font-family: "Helvetica Neue","Arial","Helvetica","Verdana",sans-serif !important;
	color: #000 !important;
	font-size: 18px !important;
	line-height: 1em !important;
	margin: 0px 8px 0px 8px !important;
	padding: 18px 18px 9px 8px !important;
	font-weight: bold !important;
	border-bottom: 1px solid #DBDBDB !important;
}
/* Content text */
.walkme-custom-balloon-content{
	font-family: "Cambria","Georgia",serif !important;
	color: #000 !important;
	font-size: 15px !important;
	line-height: 1.4em !important;
	padding: 18px 16px 16px 16px !important;
	margin: 0px !important;
}
/* Styling balloons with no buttons */
.walkme-custom-no-buttons .walkme-custom-balloon-title{
	border-bottom: none !important;
}
.walkme-custom-no-buttons .walkme-custom-balloon-buttons-wrapper{
	height: auto !important;
}
/* Disable side border & seperator */
.walkme-custom-side-border,
.walkme-custom-balloon-separator{
	display: none !important;
}
/* Centering buttons */
.walkme-custom-balloon-buttons-wrapper{
	text-align: center !important;
	height: 43px !important;
}
/* Remove back button */
.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-weak-button.walkme-custom-balloon-back-button.walkme-action-back{
	display: none !important;
}
/* Next/Done Button styling */
.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-normal-button.walkme-custom-balloon-next-button.walkme-action-next,
.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-normal-button.walkme-custom-balloon-done-button.walkme-action-done{	
	height: 25px !important;
	margin-bottom: 18px !important;
	margin-top: 0px !important;
	background: -moz-linear-gradient(#FFF, #E5E5E5) !important;
	background: -webkit-linear-gradient(#FFF, #E5E5E5) !important;
	background: -o-linear-gradient(#FFF, #E5E5E5) !important;
	background: linear-gradient(#FFF, #E5E5E5) !important;
	background-color: #E5E5E5 !important;
	border: 1px solid #CCC !important;
}
.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-normal-button.walkme-custom-balloon-next-button.walkme-action-next .walkme-custom-balloon-button-text,
.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-normal-button.walkme-custom-balloon-done-button.walkme-action-done .walkme-custom-balloon-button-text{
	font-family: "Helvetica Neue","Arial","Helvetica","Verdana",sans-serif !important;
	font-size: 12px !important;
	font-weight: 600 !important;
	color: #000 !important;
}
/* Next/Done Button - Hover state */
.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-normal-button.walkme-custom-balloon-next-button.walkme-action-next:hover,
.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-normal-button.walkme-custom-balloon-done-button.walkme-action-done:hover{
	background: -moz-linear-gradient(#FFF, #F2F2F2) !important;
	background: -webkit-linear-gradient(#FFF, #F2F2F2) !important;
	background: -o-linear-gradient(#FFF, #F2F2F2) !important;
	background: linear-gradient(#FFF, #F2F2F2) !important;
	background-color: #F2F2F2 !important;
}
/* Next/Done Button - Active state */
.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-normal-button.walkme-custom-balloon-next-button.walkme-action-next:active,
.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-normal-button.walkme-custom-balloon-done-button.walkme-action-done:active{
	background: -moz-linear-gradient(#FEFEFE, #EBEBEB) !important;
	background: -webkit-linear-gradient(#FEFEFE, #EBEBEB) !important;
	background: -o-linear-gradient(#FEFEFE, #EBEBEB) !important;
	background: linear-gradient(#FEFEFE, #EBEBEB) !important;
	background-color: #EBEBEB !important;
	box-shadow: 4px 4px 10px 0px #CCC inset !important;
}
/* Next/Done Button - Tab focus state */
.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-normal-button.walkme-custom-balloon-next-button.walkme-action-next:focus,
.walkme-custom-balloon-button.walkme-custom-balloon-normal-button.walkme-custom-balloon-done-button.walkme-action-done:focus{
	bottom: 2px solid #000 !important;
}
/* Close 'X' Icon */
.walkme-click-and-hover.walkme-action-close{
	font-size: 1px !important;
  color: transparent !important;
}
.walkme-click-and-hover.walkme-action-close::before{
	content: "" !important;
	position: absolute !important;
	background: url("https://s3-us-west-1.amazonaws.com/walkme.external/customers/FidelityExternal/X_icon15.png") !important;
	background-repeat: no-repeat !important;
	background-position: center !important;
	width: 15px !important;
	height: 15px !important;
	margin: 8px !important;
	right: 0px !important;
	top: 0px !important;
}
/* Custom BBCode Links */
.walkme-custom-bbcode-link{
	font-family: "Cambria","Georgia",serif !important;
	color: #0F57C2 !important;
	font-size: 15px !important;
	line-height: 1.4em !important;
	text-decoration: none !important;
}
.walkme-custom-bbcode-link:hover{
	cursor: pointer !important;
	text-decoration: underline !important;
}
.walkme-custom-bbcode-link:visited{
	color: #800080 !important;
	text-decoration: none !important;
}
.walkme-custom-bbcode-link:active,
.walkme-custom-bbcode-link:focus{
	color: #E74600 !important;
	text-decoration: underline !important;
}
/* Border */
.walkme-custom-balloon-inner-div{
	border: 2px #999 solid !important;
}
.walkme-custom-balloon-arrow.walkme-custom-balloon-arrow-outer{
	color: #999 !important;
}
/* Removing seperator for Title only or Content only balloons */
.walkme-custom-no-content .walkme-custom-balloon-title{
	border-bottom: 0px !important;
	padding-bottom: 16px !important;
}
.walkme-custom-no-title .walkme-custom-balloon-title{
	display: none !important;
}
/* Adjusting padding for content only balloons */
.walkme-custom-no-title .walkme-custom-balloon-content{
	padding-top: 26px !important;
}
/* Left arrow fix */
.walkme-custom-balloon-arrow.walkme-custom-balloon-arrow-inner.walkme-custom-balloon-arrow-right{
	border-color: transparent #FFFFFF transparent currentcolor !important;
}
.walkme-custom-balloon-arrow.walkme-custom-balloon-arrow-outer.walkme-custom-balloon-arrow-right{	
	border-color: transparent #999 transparent currentcolor !important;
}
/* Bottom arrow fix */
.walkme-custom-balloon-arrow.walkme-custom-balloon-arrow-top.walkme-custom-balloon-arrow-inner{
	border-color: #FFFFFF transparent !important;
}
/***** Global Balloon Design -- END *****/

						<p>Price improvement details provided for domestic stock and single leg option orders entered during market hours after the primary opening, provided there is a National Best Bid and Offer (NBBO) at the time the order is placed. Price improvement details are provided for informational purposes only and are not used for regulatory reporting purposes.</p> 

						<p>Buy market orders with a weighted average <a href="javascript:popLargerWin('https://scs.fidelity.com/webxpress/help/topics/help_definition_e.shtml#executionprice')">execution price</a> below the National Best Offer (NBO) are considered price improved. Price improvement for buy market orders is calculated by subtracting the weighted average execution price from the NBO, then multiplying by the number of executed shares to arrive at the net price improvement for the order. Price improvement on buy limit orders is calculated as the lesser of the NBO minus the execution price and the limit price minus the execution price. Sell market orders with a weighted average execution price above the National Best Bid (NBB) are considered price improved. Price improvement for sell market orders is calculated by subtracting the NBB from the weighted average execution price, then multiplying by the number of executed shares to arrive at the net price improvement for the order. Price improvement on sell limit orders is calculated as the lesser of the execution price minus the NBB and the execution price minus the limit price.</p> 
						
						<p>Prior to December 7, 2015, price improvement for limit orders (buy and sell) was calculated using the methodology for price improvement on market orders described above.</p>
